To run unity tests, you need to add Unity submodule to this directory.

Just run https://github.com/ThrowTheSwitch/Unity.git and you're good to go ;)

Ah, don't forget to export LD_LIBRARY_PATH before running the tests.

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=<parh_to_libtftp>:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH

---
TFTP TESTS
---

Run atftpd server to test the client

    $ make
    $ atftp/bin/atftpd --verbose=7 --trace --port 1234 --daemon --no-fork --logfile - /tmp/
    $ ./tftp.out